text: Pheidole noda is a species of ant in the subfamily Myrmicinae. It is found in Indonesia, Bangladesh, India, Taiwan, Thailand, Vietnam, Sri Lanka, Japan and South Korea. ==References== ==External links== * * at antwiki.org *Animaldiversity.org *Itis.org noda Category:Hymenoptera of Asia Category:Insects described in 1874
title: Pheidole noda
